      "condition": "severe (complete obstruction / imminent respiratory failure)",
      "steps": [
        "If <1 year: 5 back blows alternating with 5 chest thrusts",
        "If >1 year: Heimlich maneuver (abdominal thrusts)",
        "Activate emergency airway team simultaneously",
        "Do NOT perform blind finger sweep",
        "Once stabilized or if partial obstruction, proceed to rigid bronchoscopy",
